# Chorigen Help Center

Public documentation and tutorials for Chorigen users.

**Live Site:** https://help.chorigen.com  
**Repository:** https://github.com/chorigen-io/chorigen-help  
**Built with:** Jekyll (Ruby-based static site generator)

